						<div class="postbody">Castlevania held up great? I myself love it, still haven't beat it...or even the 3rd level, but I really enjoy it.<br /><br />And yeah, grinding is kinda annoying. There's some that get it just right and it's just enough to only make you stay in an area a little bit longer, those are always good. But agreed on stuff being lower than your lowest shot, that's a terrible design for sure.</div>

